*Dinobot could see the trees thinning out and soon broke free from their 
cover, he saw the cave and Tavatron ready at it's entrance.
He stopped then looked towards the distant cliffs that surrounded the 
valley, the run hadn't tired him a bit but the lack of sleep was beginning 
to catch up with him.
He hadn't slept a wink since he had come back to this planet and it was 
beginning to take it's toll on his systems. He made a promise to himself 
that when he got back and after the battle he would try and catch up on his 
sleep, if he had time.
Dinobot looked back at Tavatron, she looked mostly recovered and he knew 
that she could now climb the cliffs.
His own repairs had been completed before the command from Liono and he was 
now ready for battle.
Dinobot then began to walk towards the cliffs, he looked over his shoulder 
at Tavatron but turned back towards the cliffs. There was no time to be 
wasted!*

"Come!"
